oreferrer noopener\">Greece<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Culture-<\/strong> if you love to learn while on your travels, plan a trip to a country with an interesting history or well-preserved traditions. For example, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/cambodia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cambodia<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/oman\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Oman<\/a>, or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Peru<\/a>. Understanding a country&#x2019;s culture and meeting the local people is one of the best parts of traveling!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49436 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104638\/oman-travel-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\