urneys. For example, the well-renowned <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-train-kandy-ella\/\">train journey from Kandy to Ella in Sri Lanka<\/a>, the legendary motorbike loops in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/vietnam\/vietnam-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Vietnam<\/a>, or the mesmerizing silk road in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/uzbekistan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Uzbekistan<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable train travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"301\" alt=\"sustainable train travel\" class=\"wp-image-21511 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-600x402.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-800x535.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-1080x723.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-450x301.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-1536x1028.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainabl