 If you&#x2019;re visiting <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/vietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Vietnam<\/a> for the green rice paddies, go when they will be at their most lush. <\/li><li>Consider festivals and public holidays. You may want to visit a country for a particular festival, however, sometimes public holidays can cause disruption.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"salt in our hair travel philippines\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"salt in our hair travel philippines\" class=\"wp-image-22469 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23121024\/salt-in-our-hair-travel-philippines-130x163