Pinterest and Instagram<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/pinterest.com\/saltinourhair\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Pinterest<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/saltinourhair\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Instagram<\/a> are an excellent way of finding blogs and photo inspiration for destinations. Search for your destination using the hashtags or the search bar. This is a great way to find hidden gems that you otherwise might not find out about. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"how to plan a trip\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"how to plan a trip\" class=\"wp-image-49451 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104632\/how-to-plan-a-trip-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.s