m\/travel-blog\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">travel guides<\/a> based on our travel experiences ready for you! <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Find your destination here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22757&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104629\/how-to-plan-a-trip-easy-tips.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104629\/how-to-plan-a-trip-easy-tips-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104629\/how-to-plan-a-trip-easy-tips-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"How to Plan a Trip: 7 Easy Tips for Your Next Adventure\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-other-resources\">Other resources<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.com\/Profile\/SaltInOurHair\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TripAdvisor<\/a> is a great way to find recommendations for what to do and see. As well as where you want to stay or places you want to eat.<\/li><li>Google Maps, similar to TripAdvisor, offers great recommendations for food and things to do. <\/li><li>Do you know someone who has visited your destination? Ask what they did while they were there or what route they took and consider when trip planning.<\/li><li>When you arrive at your destination, ask locals for tips on what to see. <\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"plan\">4.&#xA0; Plan a Trip Itinerary&#xA0;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#x2019;ve completed your research it&#x2019;s time to put the pieces together and create a day-to-day travel itinerary. Pin the locations from your research on  Google Maps so you have a clear overview of the locations and distances between them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104649\/how-to-plan-a-trip-google-maps-507x810.jpg\" alt=\"how to plan a trip google maps\"><\/noscript><img width=\"211\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to plan a trip google maps\" class=\"wp-image-49428 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104649\/how-to-plan-a-trip-google-maps-507x810.jpg 507w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104649\/how-to-plan-a-trip-google-maps-300x479.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104649\/how-to-plan-a-trip-google-maps-600x959.jpg 600w, https:\/\