strong>Transport<\/strong>&#x2013; Where possible it&#x2019;s helpful to book transport in advance. Book online to avoid missing out once you&#x2019;re there. We book our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transportation\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">transport online here<\/a>.<br>It&#x2019;s also a good idea to use forums like Tripadvisor&#x2019;s to see the cost of transport when you&#x2019;re there. For example, how much a taxi might cost from the city center to one of the sights outside the city.<\/li><li><strong>Opening times<\/strong>&#x2013; Check the opening times of sights, so you don&#x2019;t miss out.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"luang prabang transport\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"luang prabang transport\" class=\"wp-image-23174 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/luang-prabang-transport-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/23120425\/lua