 compare the price directly from the airline. Sometimes the airline might have a promotion, so the price could be considerably cheaper. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-1080x810.jpg\" alt=\"travel blog vietnam transport\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel blog vietnam transport\" class=\"wp-image-35857 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113318\/travel-blog-vietnam-transport-1024x768.jpg 1024w, h