-sri-lanka-best-things-to-do-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-booking-accommodation\">Booking Accommodation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Use your itinerary to decide where you need accommodation and research where the best area is to stay. For example, is it best to be in the center of town close to the tourist sights, or near the beach for relaxation? Use sights like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/booking\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Booking.com<\/a> to find excellent deals and safe reviews.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-1080x795.jpg\" alt=\"Sigiriya accommodation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"331\" alt=\"Sigiriya accommodation\" class=\"wp-image-34202 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-1080x795.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-300x221.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-600x442.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-800x589.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-450x331.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112\/Sigiriya-accommodation-1536x1130.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114112