ou have contact details in case you get lost. For example, research how much a taxi will be from the airport and where to find one. Or work out which underground line you will need to get to your destination.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"322\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12158 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-600x429.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-450x322.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-800x572.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-1080x772.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-163x116.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/23142427\/travel-photography-camera-Salt-in-our-hair-iphone-252x180.jpg 252w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo